description: Safello Group AB is a SE-based company operating in Capital Markets industry. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2021-05-12. Safello Group AB is a Sweden-based cryptocurrency brokerage services company. The firm offers Bitcoin exchange for European customers. Safello Group enables customers to buy and sell with card payments, Swish and SEPA.
